  "title": "Namespace Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel' data-commentId='N:Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel'>Namespace Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel   </h1>\r\n <h3 class='section'>Namespaces</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.Archetypes.html'>Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.Archetypes</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.Events.html'>Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.Events</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section'>Classes</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.CommandBuffer.html'>CommandBuffer</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Stores a set of structual changes that can be applied to a <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.CommandBuffer.Scene\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.Component-1.html'>Component&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Used to quickly get the component ID of a given type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.Component.html'>Component</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Class for registering components</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentDelegates-1.html'>ComponentDelegates&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Used only in source generation</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section'>Structs</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.html'>AddComponent</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Add component command</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentData.html'>ComponentData</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Component metadata</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentHandle.html'>ComponentHandle</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A handle to a component of any type. Useful to avoid boxing.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentId.html'>ComponentId</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A lightweight struct that represents a component type. Used for fast lookups.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.CreateCommand.html'>CreateCommand</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Create entity command</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.DeleteComponent.html'>DeleteComponent</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Delete component command</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.GameObjectIdOnly.html'>GameObjectIdOnly</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The gameObject id only</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.GameObjectType.html'>GameObjectType</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Represents an gameObject's type, or set of component and tag types that make it up</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.Ref-1.html'>Ref&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A wrapper ref struct over a reference to a <code class=\"typeparamref\">T</code></p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section'>Interfaces</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ITypeId.html'>ITypeId</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The type id interface</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section'>Delegates</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentDelegates-1.DestroyDelegate.html'>ComponentDelegates&lt;T&gt;.DestroyDelegate</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Used only in source generation</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentDelegates-1.InitDelegate.html'>ComponentDelegates&lt;T&gt;.InitDelegate</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Used only in source generation</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
